Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.87,1:45:39.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,oboeteiru kotoba no koto\Nomoidaseru ondo no koto
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.87,1:45:50.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,nakushite kieta kesenai\Nkoto nakunaru koto ga kimatteiru koto
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.15,1:46:03.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,mou ichido mou nidoto
