Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.12,1:46:24.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,ano koe o atatakasa o
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.33,1:46:34.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,tashikamete mada shinzou ga
